nodes.val: pattern_grid = Extract a 3*3 matrix from the image matrix with (0,0) as the upper left corner and (2,2) as the lower right corner(input_grid)
pattern_grid1 = Rotate grid clockwise by 90 degrees(pattern_grid)
pattern_grid2 = Rotate grid clockwise by 90 degrees(pattern_grid1)

output_grid = Cover the 3*3 matrix in the image matrix with (0,4) as the upper left corner and (2,6) as the lower right corner with pattern_grid1, and cover the 3*3 matrix in the image matrix with (0,8) as the upper left corner and (2,10) as the lower right corner with pattern_grid2(input_grid, pattern_grid1, pattern_grid2)
